snippet: Two new restaurants with modest, occasionally boundary-crossing delights set up shop around the neighborhood’s Little Manila.
abstract: Ligaya Mishan reviews Filipino restaurants Tito King's Kitchen, at Jimmy's No 43 bar, and Bago, both in East Village.
lead_paragraph: Two new restaurants with modest, occasionally boundary-crossing delights set up shop around the neighborhood’s Little Manila.

headline.print_headline: A Growth Spurt in Little Manila
headline.main: Tito King’s Kitchen and Bago Join a Filipino Feast in the East Village
